{"tid":1332250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】7.21遊行獲發不反對通知書 警以安全為由拒金鐘或中環作終點","createTime":"2019-07-19T08:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T14:21:28.000Z","uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"79eda65cf660279a9cbf83624c51f06e51446860","tid":1332250,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:48:42.000Z","msg":"民陣於本周日7.21再次發起反送中大遊行，並於今日收到警方不反對通知書，遊行原定以中環遮打道終審法院為終點，但警方以公共秩序安全為由，嚴格限制遊行終點必須設於灣仔盧押道與莊士敦道交界，不能以金鐘或中環作終站；且當日遊行必須於當晚9點結束，有別於過往定於晚上11時59分。警方也企硬只開放軒尼詩道西行3線及兩條電車路，拒絕開放軒尼詩道6條行車線。<br />\n<br />\n7.21遊行將於下午3時集合起步，在銅鑼灣維園出發。民陣在6.9及6.16亦曾發起反送中遊行，有103萬及200萬人參與。<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190719&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59840971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190719%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59840971&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=a893739d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190719%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59840971&h=e6c360ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190719&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59840971</a>"},{"pid":"84d60c3d899cb03946ee67d19a08477fd6c5a56c","tid":1332250,"uid":73619,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣囉"},{"pid":"e89e8c2fce0385dfce25047decd3e413f32c393a","tid":1332250,"uid":196309,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:49:38.000Z","msg":"遊行完，d人照去中環金鐘"},{"pid":"484cbe29967c44eaa8812c5ac17e6ef9af23b021","tid":1332250,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba99efb5021cab972f99c18e6d8e3b7213544d9","tid":1332250,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"ifc 見"},{"pid":"bb10bb8c1cf517ca1f3dfc1aa1ee